        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Mumbai/scene_mongoose.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository fdd810a9-1f9d-4115-8ef5-3f6016e8a66b).Image",
        "Description": "Due to the fear of becoming a target of 47 Danwood Rangan has made a deal with the ICA, in wich he arranges a meeting between Vanya Shah, the Maelstrom and himself. While the meeting the ICA can kill Vanya Shah and the Maelsrtom. Unfortunately somebody hired a group of Assasins, trying to prevent Danwood Rangan from mkaing the necessary phone call for the meeting. \r47, Your Mission is to kill the Assasins, before they can get to Danwood Rangan. It&apos;s urgent, so you got no more than 5 minutes.",
